# 🧪 Python Sandbox – Experimental Visualizations

This folder contains exploratory Python scripts used to develop or test visualizations related to churn, retention, lifecycle, and cohort behavior for the Hopify SaaS KPI project.

---

## 📜 Script Index

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `hopify_burndown_chart_simulated.py` | Simulates a burndown-style retention chart using synthetic churn decay |


---

## ⚠️ Notes

- These scripts may require additional tweaking or input data (`.csv` or database access)
- Final visuals may be exported to `/visuals/` if they are clean and presentation-ready
- Recommended for internal use, prototyping, or tutorial extensions

---

## ✅ Suggested Use

- Refactor promising scripts into `/python/` main folder for clean deliverables
- Keep this folder for drafts, demos, or exploratory visual development
